title: Ubisoft - CSI NewYork - New Hidden Object Style Puzzle Adventure
description:
For the first time ever, immerse yourself in the world 
of CSI: NY. Experience five original cases written by 
CSI writers and solve mysteries alongside your favorite 
characters from the hit TV crime show.
* SOLVE CRIMES IN THE BIG APPLE - Finally, 
CSI fans can experience the environment, characters 
and mysteries of CSI: NY. Piece together clues and 
uncover hidden evidence in the biggest city in America. 
Explore five brand-new, bizarre crimes and bring suspects 
to justice.
